title: Secret Of Mana Theater (2002-2007) -WackyAnimation-
description:
This is the longest running Flash series on the web, and a great tribute to an awesome SNES game. The story is told primarily with the original sprites and follows a spin off story close to the original. I recommend playing the game first, but that is in no way necessary.

I hope you enjoy this often hilarious series as much as I do.

Normal Episodes: 285
Special Episodes: 46
Total Episodes: 322

Enjoy -WackyAnimation
